sources.title: Running Wild, The Life of Dayton O. Hyde (full documentary) wild horse sanctuary
sources.description:
Dayton O. Hyde is one of the last great American cowboys.  Through heroic determination, he single-handedly rescues the wild mustang from government slaughter on his breathtaking twelve thousand acre Black Hills Wild Horse Sanctuary.

Directed by Suzanne Mitchell
2013
Starring Dayton O. Hyde, Susan Watt, Tom Cook, Andrew Hyde
